headline: The 5 Most Interesting Analyst Questions From DexCom’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: DexCom’s fourth quarter results reflected ongoing momentum in both product innovation and international expansion. Management attributed the quarter’s performance to the broad rollout of the G7 15-day sensor system in the U.S., which generated positive initial feedback from both customers and physicians due to improved wear time and accuracy. Operational improvements in manufacturing and logistics, such as reestablishing more efficient ocean shipping routes and addressing prior sensor deployment
